Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你终于看这边了呐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:02:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望兄长你能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给桐山一个警示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小少爷那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想起他说的话真是才…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\fad(2000,0)\pos(176,298)}耀眼之暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被他催促着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后看着棋盘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快就恢复了状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棋面就是这么糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先感受到冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后感受到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和暴风雨一样的 羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我怎么看这个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这种类型的人对局时间会很长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅长呐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫「这种人」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能慌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被他抓住机会的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为自己是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说着不能慌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底看错了多少个等级啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想着要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想等着别人失误的棋手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在心里随意计算别人的等级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能在这里倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都看不穿别人的棋力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己内心充满私怨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把A级棋手当成杂鱼对待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑的 耀眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他轻轻地咳嗽了一声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道是在对我说「冷静下来」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续被他催促着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用混乱的头脑拼命的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找着下一步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我蔑视他的事也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今我注意到这点而感到惊慌也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人全部 全部看穿了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静静地坐在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在这里因为羞耻而半途逃走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是真正的任意妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中仅存的一点决心 继续对局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 没有任何悬念 对局结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 开始分析战局
